Description: Implementation of a production frontier model based on the three-step estimation approach described in "A Three-Step Approach to Production Frontier Estimation and the Matsuokaâ€™s Distribution" article. This package provides tools for estimating the production frontier, evaluating efficiency, and visualizing results. Various methods for nonparametric regression estimation of the `g(x)` function are supported, including local linear regression, splines, generalized additive models, classical backfitting, etc...
